[assistant] Cause:
[assistant] - The test set `org.modelmapper.internal.bytebuddy.safe=true` before loading the `UsingReflection` superclass.
[assistant] - That superclass initialization can cache Byte Buddy’s unsafe dispatcher availability while unsafe access is disabled, so the later nested static block setting the property to `false` was too late.
